Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Health Care Facilities & Svcs
Sub-Industry: Health Care Services
Aramark Healthcare Technologies, LLC provides clinical equipment inventory maintenance and management services. The Company offers evidence based clinical equipment, logistical programs, supply chain, and workforce management services. Aramark Healthcare Technologies serves its clients in the United States.




