Aramark Healthcare Technologies LLC



 OVERVIEW



Date Founded


2007




Headquarters


160 Mine Lake Court, Suite 200, Raleigh, NC 27615




Industries


Wholesale: Medical Supplies & Pharmaceuticals

Medical Products & Equipment




Company Description


ARAMARK Healthcare Technologies LLC provides biomedical and diagnostic imaging service solutions. It offers on-site and demand-based services for evidence-based clinical equipment inventory maintenance and management. The company was founded on August 14, 2007 and is headquartered in Downers Grove, IL






